kâh-kisiwâhtwâw
;
He was the object of many people's anger;

iskwêyâc êkwah ômis êsah itêw nôtokêwa pêyak êh-ayâwâcik :
nôhkô , pêsiw kitihkom , itêw êsah ;
êkotôwah nik-ôh-nipahâwak , itwêw êsah . At the end of this time he spoke thus to a certain old woman whom they had with them: “Grandmother, give me a louse of yours,” he said to her; “With such I shall kill them,” he said.
